<p><b>  Report of the Special Rapporteur on the sale of children, 
child prostitution and child pornography, Ms. Najat M&#8217;jid 
Maalla 
</b></p>
<p> <i>Summary</i> 
 The Special Rapporteur on the sale of children, child prostitution and child 
pornography, Ms. Najat M&#8217;jid Maalla, submits her second report to the Human Rights 
Council at its sixteenth session, pursuant to resolution 13/20 of the Council. 
</p>
<p> The present report describes the activities carried out by the Special Rapporteur 
since her last report in September 2009. 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
<p> 
</p>
